io.reinert.requestor.core

Interface IncomingResponse

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DeserializableResponse, DeserializableResponseInProcess, MutableResponse, MutableSerializedResponse, ProcessableResponse, Response, ResponseInProcess, SerializedResponse, SerializedResponseInProcess
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RawResponse

    public interface IncomingResponse
    Represents a raw HTTP response.
    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
